Uses of Package
enums

Packages that use enums
Package
Description
controller
Contains all the necessary classes to manage the information between the view clases and the model classes.
enums
Contains all the enumerated classes which determine the status or type of the model classes.
helper
Contains two classes, Excel and OptionChecker.
